.Dd $Mdocdate: January 11 2024 $
.Dt managedeventsd 8
.Os macOS
.Sh NAME
.Nm managedeventsd
.Nd Device Management Endpoint Security client daemon
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.Nm
.Sh DESCRIPTION
.Nm
monitors disk mount events and process execution events via Endpoint Security API. It responds to mount and process launch requests based on restriction policies from the Device Management system.
.Sh FILES
.Pa /System/Library/LaunchDaemons/com.apple.devicemanagementclient.managedeventsd.plist
.Sh DIAGNOSTICS
Logging can be viewed via:
log stream --predicate 'process="managedeventsd"'

